hopobject.body: What line of work are you in? physician order entry pharmacy Life begins at birth, dupes of Hell; it always did, with the first breath of life, soul, and humanity God breathes into each of us, exactly as He did Adam. It made no differnece when the lump of clay had a beating heart, and it makes no difference today. God makes life; not a man and woman during a rut, no matter how intense the orgasm and how appealing to human ego.
